<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1679422-i-have-reread-the-ending-three-times-did">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I have reread the ending three times. Did the child die? Were there one or two Tims...it seems like there are three different endings. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
