<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1679422-i-have-reread-the-ending-three-times-did">2 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1679422-i-have-reread-the-ending-three-times-did">See all 5 answers</a>
</li>
