</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/40726587-denise"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_100x100-6433b08cbe793211f55e184d39e84c4d.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/40726587-denise">Denise</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    SPOILER ALERT: Well I read the last chapter 3 times also!! Here is what my take on it is: Abbie takes Danny and goes to Northhaven thinking it is an a<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    SPOILER ALERT: Well I read the last chapter 3 times also!! Here is what my take on it is: Abbie takes Danny and goes to Northhaven thinking it is an autism school/farm where the real Abbie is living and in hiding. To her surprise, when she and Danny enter the house [which is an exact replica of the beach house in CA] Tim appears and says Welcome Abbie...he knew she would be coming....but it is a robot Tim, not the real live one. And Abbie is very confused as was I!! And then, just coming up behind her is the REAL live Tim...so now there are two Tim's; one robot, one alive. And there is only one Abbie...the robot. Tim makes her remember through her memory function that he killed the real Abbie at their beach house because he realized she was going to leave him. In the next few years, he made a robot of himself and built this house, for Tim the robot and Abbie the robot and Danny would be in the ABA school with very harsh and unlimited aversives. Abbie is horrified at this. He wants to retrain Abbie into a submissive and fun girl and will have to reboot her. She is of course, not up for this plan.<br /><br />Abbie takes Danny out to the beach after this meeting with the 2 Tim's and takes his hand and walks into the ocean. You think that she is going to drown him and she will be destroyed by the water. <br /><br />But then....OK, here is where I get a little confused. A boat comes roaring up with Charles Carter [the neighbor from the original beach house], Lisa and Jenny on board. They were told where to find her by "we"...in Chapter 26. I don't know who the "we" are. But they get there just in time...Abbie hands Danny into the boat, they hand Abbie a pile of Danny's clothes, the boat roars away and Abbie gets destroyed. <br /><br />At the house, Tim the robot feels the disconnect of Abbie and realizes that she is destroyed. The real Tim is told and he is devastated. So, robot Tim goes into the closet and pulls out another Abbie robot to cheer Tim up. <br /><br />If anyone out there knows who the "we" are in Chapter 26 who told the people in the boat where Abbie and Danny were, please let me know!<br /><a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
</div>
