<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1642067-explain-the-ending-please">Explain the ending, please?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1642067'><a id="like_count_community_question_1642067" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1642067?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F42927050-the-perfect-wife">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1642067-explain-the-ending-please">2 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1642067-explain-the-ending-please">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/65280581-k17a17s"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/65280581-k17a17s">K17a17s</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    SPOILERS....<br /><br />The real Tim killed the real Abbie because she was planning to take Danny and leave him.<br /><br />The real Tim then made two cobots -- Abbie (which <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    SPOILERS....<br /><br />The real Tim killed the real Abbie because she was planning to take Danny and leave him.<br /><br />The real Tim then made two cobots -- Abbie (which we are introduced to right away) and Tim (which we discover at the end of the book). It sounds like the real Tim planned to the have the two cobots teach/train Danny.<br /><br />The cobot Abbie was set up by Tim so that her thoughts could be read. However, Jenny switched that up when Abbie went to meet with Mike -- that allowed Abbie to have some independent thoughts that were not readable by Tim (and fooled Tim with "fake" thoughts).<br /><br />It appears that the cobot Abbie knew that the real Abbie would not be in North Haven and made a plan with the real Abbie's sister and Charles to drown herself and have them escape with Danny (leaving Tim to believe that Danny drowned too). It is not clear how/when Abbie realized that Tim was setting her up about North Haven and put this plan into action. The story reads as if the cobot Abbie really believed that she was going to North Haven to see the real Abbie and possibly kill her. But, I am thinking this plan for the boat to come save Danny had to be pre-arranged.<br /><br />Anyway, the co-bot Abbie is dead/gone from oversurge of the water from the ocean. The real Tim is devastated because he thinks that Danny is dead too. The cobot Tim thinks about one day killing Tim and assuming his life -- but, in the meantime, the cobot Tim indicates that he is going to activite another cobot Abbie and have that cycle start again. I expect that the real Tim or the cobot Tim would also ultimately create a cobot Danny but that isn't stated in the book.<br /><br />This was a very very very weird book but I've got to say that the author committed 110% to it.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
</div>
